com.betfair.cougar.codegen

Interface NodeExcluder


  • public interface NodeExcluder
    Use an instance of this interface to describe how you'd omit a particular transformation from being run. The @see Transformation class does not provide any functionality to prevent a class from being generated.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      boolean exclude(XPath xp, Node node)
      Implement this method to return true if a node SHOULD be omitted from having a transformation run against it.

    • Method Detail

      • exclude

        Implement this method to return true if a node SHOULD be omitted from having a transformation run against it.
        Parameters:
        xp - an instanciated XPath instance
        node - to use to determine whether this transformation should be run or not
        Returns:
        returns true if the transformation should be omitted
